text: Henry Wahl (9 March 1915 – 13 October 1984) was a Norwegian speed skater. He competed in the 10,000 m event at the 1948 Winter Olympics, but failed to finish. He was Norwegian all-round champion in 1947. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1984 deaths Category:People from Hordaland Category:Norwegian male speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Norway Category:Speed skaters at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:World Allround Speed Skating Championships medalists
